                        <fn>William E.</fn>
                        <sf/>
                        <pf/>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>Charles P. Lambert and Miss Sallie B. Burdet, both of Staunton, were
                    married on November 17th by the Rev. William E. Baker.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
